'''Urang Melayu'''<ref name="Malayan miscellanies">{{en}}{{cite book|first=Malayan miscellanies | last=Malayan miscellanies | title=''[http://books.google.co.id/books?id=fBYIAAAAQAAJ&dq=dayak%20Malayan%20miscellanies&pg=RA1-PA51#v=onepage&q&f=false Malayan miscellanies ]'' | publisher=Malayan miscellanies | year=1820}}</ref><ref name="Anthony Milner">{{en}}{{cite book|first=[[Anthony Milner|Anthony]] | last=Milner | coauthors= | title=''[http://books.google.co.id/books?id=sACaolB0FpkC&lpg=PP1&dq=Malays&pg=PP1#v=onepage&q&f=false The Malays]'' | publisher=John Wiley and Sons | year=2010 | isbn=9781444339031 }}ISBN 1444339036</ref> adolah namo nan marujuak pado suatu kalompok nan ciri utamonyo adolah panutuaan [[bahaso Melayu]]. Bahaso Melayu iolah anggota kaluargo bahaso Austronesia. Urang Melayu bamukim di sabagian basa [[Malaysia]], pasisia timua [[Sumatera]], sakaliliang pasisia [[Kalimantan]], Thailand Selatan, sarato pulau-pulau ketek nan tabantang sapanjang [[Selat Malaka]] jo [[Selat Karimata]]. Di Indonesia, jumlah urang Melayu sakita 15% dari saluruah populasi, nan sabagian basa mandiami propinsi [[Sumatera Utaro]], [[Riau]], [[Kapulauan Riau]], [[Jambi]], [[Sumatera Selatan]], [[Kapulauan Bangka Belitung|Bangka Belitung]], jo [[Kalimantan Barat]].<ref>{{cite book |title=Indonesia's Population, Ethnicity and Religion in a Changing Political Landscape |last=Suryadinata |first=Leo |authorlink= |coauthors=Arifin, Evi Nurvidya; Ananta, Aris|year=2003 |publisher=Institute of Southeast Asian Studies |location= |isbn=981-230-212-3 |page= |pages= |url= |accessdate=}}</ref> Kumpuaan urang atau etnik Melayu balainan dari konsep Rumpun Bangso Melayu, nan mancakuik'i kumpuaan manusia nan labiah laweh, tamasuak kabanyakan etnik di Indonesia jo Filipina. 

Meskipun baitu, banyak pulo masyarakaik [[Suku Minangkabau|Minangkabau]], [[Suku Mandailing|Mandailing]], jo [[Suku Dayak|Dayak]] nan bapindah ka wilayah pasisia timua Sumatra jo pantai baraik Kalimantan, mangaku sabagai urang Melayu. Salain di Nusantara, urang Melayu tadapaik pulo di [[Sri Lanka]], [[Kapulauan Cocos (Keeling)]] (''Cocos Malays''), jo [[Afrika Selatan]] (''Cape Malays'').

